lock text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">Pricing</a> <a href="/about" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">About</a> <a href="/legal" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">Legal</a> <div class="pt-2 border-t border-gray-200"> <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">More Info</p> <a href="/news" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">News</a> <a href="/guide" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">How-to Guide</a> <a href="/resources" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">Other Resources</a> <a href="/contact" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">Contact</a> </div> </div> </div> </header> <script type="module">const e=document.getElementById("mobile-menu-button"),t=document.getElementById("mobile-menu");e?.addEventListener("click",()=>{t?.classList.toggle("hidden")});</script> -  <div id="version-banner" class="bg-green-600 text-white text-center py-2 px-4 text-sm hidden"> <span>Welcome to the new BunTool! It  has recently been upgraded to improve privacy. If you have any comments or  thoughts about the new app, please <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#cebabca7bd8ebda6abbca2a7a5abbce0a0abba" class="underline font-semibold hover:text-blue-200">share them by email</a></span>.
<button onclick="this.parentElement.classList.add('hidden')" class="ml-4 text-blue-200 hover:text-white font-bold">&times;</button> </div> <script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script type="module">new Date<new Date("2026-05-01")&&document.getElementById("version-banner")?.classList.remove("hidden");</script> <main style="zoom: 0.8"> <!-- Hero Section --> <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-700 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden"> <!-- Background Image --> <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30"> <img src="/images/filesonshelf.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> </div> <!-- Content --> <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto"> <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-0 gap-x-8 md:gap-8 items-center"> <!-- Text — first on mobile, second (right) on desktop --> <div class="order-1 md:order-2 text-center md:text-left px-4 pt-8 pb-0 md:py-0"> <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
BunTool: Make legal bundles in minutes, for free
</h1> <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-200 mb-8">
Organise your court papers <strong>privately, simply and accurately</strong>. Get it right every time.
</p> <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start mb-8"> <a href="/app" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-pink-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-pink-600 transition duration-150"> <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path> </svg>
Try Creating a Bundle Now
</a> <a href="/guide" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-slate-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-slate-600 transition duration-150">
How-to Guide
</a> </div> </div> <!-- Hero animation — second on mobile (below text), first (left) on desktop --> <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex justify-center md:justify-start"> <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full max-h-90 md:max-h-[42rem] object-contain rounded-lg shadow-xl"> <source src="/images/buntool-animation-web.webm" type="video/webm"> <img src="/images/example-bundle.png" alt="Example BunTool bundle" class="w-full max-h-90 md:max-h-[42rem] object-contain rounded-lg shadow-xl"> </video> </div> </div> </div> </section> <hr class="border-gray-200"> <!-- How Does It Work --> <section class="py-6 bg-white"> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4"> <div class="text-center mb-16"> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How does it work?</h2> </div> <!-- Text and Image Layout --> <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start mb-12"> <!-- Text on Left --> <div class="flex-1 text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-4"> <p>
BunTool is a free way to create PDF legal bundles on your own computer. "Bundles" are organised sets of documents for use in court or other legal settings. It can be difficult to comply with the various court rules, and can take hours to do it properly: BunTool solves the problem, and it's free for anyone to use.
</p> <p>
The bundles are designed to comply with the requirements for courts and tribunals in England and Wales, but may also be useful elsewhere.
</p> </div> <!-- Images side by side --> <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-end"> <img src="/images/merge-pdfs.png" alt="Merge PDFs" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" style="height:250px;width:auto;"> <img src="/images/example-bundle.png" alt="Example BunTool bundle" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" style="height:250px;width:auto;"> </div> </div> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8"> <!-- Step 1 --> <div class="text-center"> <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-700 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">1</div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Select documents</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">Choose what goes into your bundle. They stay on your device.</p> </div> <!-- Step 2 --> <div class="text-center"> <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-700 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">2</div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Review and configure</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">Review interactive index, choose title and other details</p> </div> <!-- Step 3 --> <div class="text-center"> <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-700 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">3</div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">All handled locally</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">Bundle created without uploading data</p> </div> <!-- Step 4 --> <div class="text-center"> <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-700 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">4</div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Save the results</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">Bundle is ready in seconds</p> </div> </div> <div class="text-center mt-12"> <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
Read the <a href="/guide" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900 underline font-medium">how-to guide</a> or just <a href="/app" class="text-pink-600 hover:text-pink-700 underline font-medium">try creating a bundle now</a>.
</p> </div> </div> </section> <hr class="border-gray-200"> <!-- Privacy and Freedom --> <section class="py-6 bg-gray-50"> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4"> <div class="text-center mb-12"> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy and Freedom</h2> </div> <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700"> <p> <strong>BunTool respects your privacy.</strong> It's here to help court hearings run more smoothly, not a data farm: we don't want your private information. BunTool is designed to make sure your data stays on your machine:
</p><ul> <li><svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> No login or account needed
</li><li> <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> No uploading of any files or information
</li><li> <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Files stay private on your device
</li><li> <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> No third party processing
</li><li> <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> No data collection
</li><li> <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> No cookies
</li></ul>
It's just a tool you can use. That's why there's no cookie banner or GDPR notice: We comply with GDPR by not recording your data. For more information, see the <a href="/legal" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900 underline font-medium">Privacy information</a>.
 <div class="text-center mt-8"> <a href="/app" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-pink-500 hover:bg-pink-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg transition"> <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path> </svg>
Create Bundle
</a> </div> </div> </div> </section> <hr class="border-gray-200"> <!-- Features Section --> <section id="features" class="py-6 bg-white"> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4"> <div class="text-center mb-12"> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">BunTool Features</h2> </div> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8"> <!-- Feature 1 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">100% private</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">No tracking. Your files never leave your device. All processing happens in your browser with no uploads.</p> </div> <!-- Feature 2 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Completely free</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">No subscriptions, no hidden fees, no limits. BunTool is Open Source software, made to be free for everyone: not just individuals and charities, but law firms, barristers, mediators and even courts themselves."
</p> </div> <!-- Feature 3 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Perfect PDF Bundles</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">Hyperlinked, bookmarked, and indexed ready for court use—with perfect page numbering.</p> </div> <!-- Feature 4 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Automatic Index</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">BunTool formats and creates an index automatically for you. No need to fiddle with tables or calculate page numbers.</p> </div> <!-- Feature 5 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Extremely simple to use</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">All you need to do is add your PDFs and type in basic information like the case name: everything else is handled for you in seconds, making completely court-compliant PDFs.</p> </div> <!-- Feature 6 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition"> <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"> <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Great for court, meetings, conferences and more</h3> <p class="text-gray-600">The default settings work with the English court rules - but it's also customisable.</p> </div> </div> </div> </section> <hr class="border-gray-200"> <!-- Pricing Section --> <section id="pricing" class="py-6 bg-gray-50"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4"> <div class="text-center mb-12"> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Pricing</h2> <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center mb-8"> <div class="inline-block bg-white border-4 border-pink-500 rounded-2xl p-12 shadow-xl"> <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">£0</div> <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Unlimited</div> </div> <div class="inline-block bg-white border-4 border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl"> <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Want to support BunTool?</div> <a href="https://ko-fi.com/buntool" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-pink-500 hover:bg-pink-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg transition">
Donate on Ko-fi
</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700"> <p> <strong>It's free and open source</strong>: you don't have to pay. It's about access to justice, not money. To understand more about free software licence read more about what free software means <a href="/about#free-software" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900 underline font-medium">on the Legal page</a> or click on the green Open Source Initiatve logo:
</p> <div class="flex justify-center"> <a href="https://opensource.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <img src="/images/free.png" alt="Open Source Software" class="mx-auto" style="height:150px;width:auto;"> </a> </div> <p>
If you appreciate BunTool and would like to contribute to the running costs, please consider <a href="https://ko-fi.com/buntool" class="text-pink-600 hover:text-pink-700 underline font-medium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">making a donation</a>.
</p> </div> </div> </section> <hr class="border-gray-200"> <!-- Testimonials Section --> <section class="py-12 bg-white"> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4"> <div class="text-center mb-12"> <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What People Are Saying About BunTool...</h2> </div> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"> <!-- Testimonial 1 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm"> <div class="mb-4"> <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"> <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"></path> </svg> </div> <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">"Just a quick note to thank you for your helpful Buntool, which I have been using to quickly create bundles in a matter involving a significant number of documents. It has truly saved me hours of my life."</p> <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">— A Senior barrister</p> </div> <!-- Testimonial 2 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm"> <div class="mb-4"> <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"> <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"></path> </svg> </div> <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">"I am currently a litigant in person in a civil case - your product has been brilliant because reading the court rules on preparing paginated bundles is like reading something written in double dutch."</p> <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">— A Litigant in Person</p> </div> <!-- Testimonial 3 --> <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-5